  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Similar in appearance to soup crackers, when under its influence the user has increased fine motor control and spacial awareness.</p><p><strong>Primary Effect</strong></p><ul><li><p>Dose lasts 4 hours</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>For the duration of the effect, the user's DEX increases by 1 point. This can raise your DEX above 8. In addition, they are prone to involuntary spasmatic movements.</p></li><li><p>For the duration of the Primary Effect, your GM will occasionally tell you when you feel a twitch coming on, and you should do your best to roleplay accordingly.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Secondary Effect (DV15)</strong></p><ul><li><p>If the user wasn't already addicted to Mumbo Jumbo, they are now. While addicted, their DEX is lowered by 2 points, unless the user is currently experiencing the primary effect of Mumbo Jumbo.</p></li><li><p>While addicted to Mumbo Jumbo, your GM will occasionally tell you when you crave more Mumbo Jumbo, and you should do your best to roleplay accordingly.</p></li></ul>"
    },
